rue":false,"questionId":11421,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">支气管肺癌</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":51296,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-07-01 11:19:34","updateTime":"2019-07-01 11:19:34","isTrue":false,"questionId":11421,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">肺结核</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":928,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:26","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:26","name":"182","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46},{"id":935,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:29:57","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:29:57","name":"呼吸A3","questionCnt":14,"tagTypeId":47}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":10762,"createTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","topicId":null,"tagId":927,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":124,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女孩，</span>2岁。发热伴咳嗽、咳痰4天，查体:T38.8℃,P132次/分，R12次/分，轻度鼻扇，双肺闻及中细湿啰音,腹稍胀，肝肋下2cm。胸部X线片见双下肺模糊裹片状影。实验室检查，WBC13.5×10</span><sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px;vertical-align:super\">9</span></sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">/L,N0.72,L0.28。</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">治疗中患儿呼吸困难加重，呕吐少许咖啡样物。查体</span>:P140次/分，R46次/分，严重腹胀，听诊肠鸣音消失。考虑患儿最可能发生了</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">严重者发生缺氧中毒性肠麻痹时</span>,表现为频繁呕吐、严重腹胀、呼吸困难加重听诊肠鸣音消失。重症患儿还可呕吐咖啡样物,大便潜血阳性或柏油样便。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":47999,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","updateTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","isTrue":true,"questionId":10762,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">中毒性肠麻痹</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":48000,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","updateTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","isTrue":false,"questionId":10762,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">感染性体克</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":48001,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","updateTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","isTrue":false,"questionId":10762,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">脑性低钠血症</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":48002,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","updateTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","isTrue":false,"questionId":10762,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">中毒性脑病</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":48003,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","updateTime":"2019-06-29 14:01:06","isTrue":false,"questionId":10762,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">心力衰竭</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":935,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:29:57","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:29:57","name":"呼吸A3","questionCnt":14,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":10759,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","topicId":null,"tagId":927,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":123,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女孩，</span>2岁。发热伴咳嗽、咳痰4天，查体:T38.8℃,P132次/分，R12次/分，轻度鼻扇，双肺闻及中细湿啰音,腹稍胀，肝肋下2cm。胸部X线片见双下肺模糊裹片状影。实验室检查，WBC13.5×10</span><sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px;vertical-align:super\">9</span></sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">/L,N0.72,L0.28。</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">首选的治疗药物是</span></span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">支气管肺炎多见于金黄色葡萄球菌感染，根据不同病原选择抗菌药物</span>:①肺炎链球菌:青霉素敏感者首选青霉素或阿莫西林;青霉素中介者,首选大剂量青霉素或阿莫西林;耐药者首选头孢曲松、头孢噻肟、万古霉素;青霉素过敏者选用大环内酯类抗生素，如红霉素等。②金黄色葡萄球菌:甲氧西林敏感者首选苯唑西林钠或氯唑西林,耐药者选用万古霉索或联用利福平。③流感嗜血杆菌:首选阿莫西林/克拉维酸、氨苄西林/舒巴坦、④大肠埃希菌和肺炎克雷伯杆菌:不产超广谱β内酰胺酶(ESBLs)菌首选头孢他啶、头孢哌酮;产ESBLs菌首选亚胺培南、美罗培南;⑤铜绿假单胞菌(绿脓杆菌)首选替卡西林/克拉维酸 &nbsp;⑥卡他莫拉菌:首选阿莫西林/克拉维酸;⑦肺炎支原体和衣原体:首选大环内酯类抗生素.如阿奇霉素、红霉素及罗红霉素。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":47984,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","updateTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","isTrue":false,"questionId":10759,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">阿奇霉素</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":47985,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","updateTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","isTrue":false,"questionId":10759,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">万古霉素</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":47986,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","updateTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","isTrue":true,"questionId":10759,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">苯唑西林钠</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":47987,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","updateTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","isTrue":false,"questionId":10759,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">阿莫西林</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":47988,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","updateTime":"2019-06-29 13:59:33","isTrue":false,"questionId":10759,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">利巴韦林</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":935,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:29:57","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:29:57","name":"呼吸A3","questionCnt":14,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":10757,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","topicId":null,"tagId":927,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":122,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女孩，</span>2岁。发热伴咳嗽、咳痰4天，查体:T38.8℃,P132次/分，R12次/分，轻度鼻扇，双肺闻及中细湿啰音,腹稍胀，肝肋下2cm。胸部X线片见双下肺模糊裹片状影。实验室检查，WBC13.5×10</span><sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px;vertical-align:super\">9</span></sup><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">/L,N0.72,L0.28。</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">最可能的诊断是</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">支气管肺炎的诊断比较简单</span>,一般有发热、咳嗽、呼吸急促的症状,肺部听诊闻及中、细湿啰音和(或)胸部影像学有肺炎的改变均可诊断为支气管肺炎。</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">（</span>1）急性支气管炎：一般不发热或仅有低热，全身情况好，以咳嗽为主要症状，肺部可闻及干湿啰音,多不固定，随咳嗽而改变。x线示肺纹理增多、排列紊乱。若鉴别困难,则按肺炎处理。（2）大叶性肺炎：临床起病多急骤,可有寒战、高热可达40℃.呼吸急促呼气呻吟鼻翼扇动、发绀,可有胸痛,最初数日多咳嗽不重，无痰,后可有痰呈铁锈色。轻症者神志清醒,重症者可有烦躁、嗜睡、惊厥、谵妄,甚至昏迷等缺氧中毒性脑病表现。亦可伴发休克、急性呼吸窘迫综合征等</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">（</span>3）毛细支气管炎：本病常发生于2岁以下小儿，多数在6个月以内,常为首次发作。喘息和肺部哮鸣音为其突出表现。主要表现为下呼吸道梗阻症状,出现呼气性呼吸困难、呼气相延长伴喘息。呼吸困难可呈阵发性,间歇期喘息消失。严重发作者,可见面色苍白、烦躁不安，口周和口唇发绀。全身中毒症状较轻,少见高热。体格检查发现呼吸浅而快, 60-80次/分,甚至100次/分,伴鼻翼扇动和三凹征;心率加快,可达150-200次/分。肺部体征主要为呼气相哮鸣音,亦可闻及中细湿啰音,叩诊可呈过清音。肝脾可由于肺过度充气而推向肋缘下,因此可触及肝和脾。重度喘憋者可有PaO</span><sub><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px;vertical-align:sub\">2</span></sub><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">降低，</span>PaCO</span><sub><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px;vertical-align:sub\">2</span></sub><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">升高。本病高峰期在呼吸困难发生后的</span>48-72小时,病程一般约为1-2周。（4）间质性肺炎：多于50岁以后发病，呈隐匿起病，主要表现为活动性呼吸困难，渐进性加重，常伴千咳。全身症状不明显,可以有不适、乏力和体重减轻等，但很少发热。75%有吸烟史。约半数患者可见杵状指(趾),90%的患者可在双肺基底部闻及吸气末细小的Velcro啰音。在疾病晚期可出现明显发绀、肺动脉高压和右心功能不全征象。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":47974,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","updateTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","isTrue":false,"questionId":10757,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">支气管炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":47975,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","updateTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","isTrue":true,"questionId":10757,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">支气管肺炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":47976,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","updateTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","isTrue":false,"questionId":10757,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">间质性肺炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":47977,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","updateTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","isTrue":false,"questionId":10757,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">毛细支气管炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":47978,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","updateTime":"2019-06-29 13:58:09","isTrue":false,"questionId":10757,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">大叶性肺炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":935,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:29:57","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:29:57","name":"呼吸A3","questionCnt":14,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null}]}